title: Fleming County students visit Early College Program (Morehead State University)
text: ( Source : Morehead State University ) Students from Fleming County High School visited the Morehead State University campus, as part of the Early College Program , Wednesday, Oct. 21. More than 50 high and technical schools offered MSU classes
